elements.name: Create new project with invalid user as manager

steps.name: I want to open browser
I want to maximize window
I want to go to OOB
I want to verify I'm in OOB main page
I want to go to projects list
I want to verify project list page
I want to click Add new project button
I want to fill project name
I want to select project type
I want to select project expected start date
I want to select project expected end date
I want to fill project budget
I want to select from owner deopdown list
I want to fill project manager field with user that is not existed
I want to tap enter key on manager field
I want to fill project owner field
I want to tap enter key on owner field
I want to fill project sponser field
I want to tap enter key on sponser field
I want to fill project description field
I want to fill project notes field
I want to add attachment for the project
I want to wait
I want to click on send project button
